overview: Captain Nemo has built a fantastic submarine for his mission of revenge. He has traveled over 20,000 leagues in search of Charles Denver - a man who caused the death of Princess Daaker. Seeing what he had done, Denver took the daughter to his yacht and sailed away.
tagline: The First Submarine Photoplay Ever Filmed
cast: Allen Holubar|Jane Gail|Howard Crampton|Matt Moore|William Welsh
